<SYNC Start=140683><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=143647><P Class=KRCC>
늦어요! 전령아저씨!
<SYNC Start=145553><P Class=KRCC>
머..먼저 가!!
<SYNC Start=147212><P Class=KRCC>
